author: Wippioo

text: Had some friends over yesterday, some of them also make music so we challenged ourselves to each make something in a short amount of time. We also decided to take the base of an existing song and make it sound completely different to add some challenge, and it did since I found it harder to compose melodies freely. Still, I'm pretty happy with the result, but I'd definitely like to revisit it. The existing song I based this on is Place de la République from Coeur de Pirate. I learned a couple days ago that she's composing the music for Child of Light, a great looking RPG from Ubisoft that's coming out soon.
